{"tid":1073954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人真係相信世界上有鬼?","createTime":"2019-03-23T05:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T06:31:17.000Z","uid":242807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf30b1c8ecc7dfc3d1fe3613a5a3e967d23f647","tid":1073954,"uid":242807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"記得好耐之前我的老母話佢唔會食牛，然後我問點解，後來發現原來有段故。<br />\n<br />\n當時我的年齡只有2~3歲，記得好似係清明節，親戚要我一起去上山拜祭祖先，所以家人只好帶我一齊上去，當時政府未整行山徑，所以我地半爬半行上去，之後發現因為有一些墳場墓碑在路線上，起初我母親唔上踏上人地D墓碑，但係我班親戚最後決定踏上去，所以我們只好跟隨着..。<br />\n<br />\n拜完山的第二天，我突然患上了一場大病，然後入了醫院住。我母親話我當時唔肯食野，然後醫生話如果再唔食野就要吊鹽水，我母親話見到隔離D病人吊鹽水好慘，所以佢向觀音娘娘說她永不食牛求我快點康復，然後相隔一會，我終於肯食野，接著慢慢康復了。<br />\n<br />\n到了現在真的覺得好不可思議，果D咩神咩鬼起初我都不相信的，但係有時真係覺得幾恐怖下..<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751df2f5923c5b619c5cf389223b5e0dcc0c66eb","tid":1073954,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:20:05.000Z","msg":"鬼定神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d71c38e7f5f15ea8196dae39e2a280a70ea42e","tid":1073954,"uid":242807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"751df2f5923c5b619c5cf389223b5e0dcc0c66eb","tid":1073954,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:20:05.000Z","msg":"鬼定神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:23:13.000Z","msg":"鬼同神都差不多姐，都係迷信.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4df205204f7c6aba710b2b11e449f5b5f8487b9","tid":1073954,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:23:30.000Z","msg":"捉鬼用保鮮紙，打鬼用朱古力"},{"pid":"4e406abd42a4d626401f1ae7e475de8cffd8b2ab","tid":1073954,"uid":242807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e4df205204f7c6aba710b2b11e449f5b5f8487b9","tid":1073954,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:23:30.000Z","msg":"捉鬼用保鮮紙，打鬼用朱古力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"星爺?<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1mKYein.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1mKYein.gif&h=0307906f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8156d09fa0214abe1bdfcd905fa8e6a58bbb2f4f","tid":1073954,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"聽落有啲戇鳩<br />\n不過你媽真係好錫你"},{"pid":"282f83d82bc2d2d2d1cc4edbc64557d4bc2776e4","tid":1073954,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:13:16.000Z","msg":"睇過幾次啦係高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本就無鬼<br />\n世上總係有啲人創啲嘢出黎<br />\n有啲人就為搵錢 好似耶撚咁 偽造啲見證 神蹟<br />\n有啲就打下上電台 刷存在感 滿足感<br />\n有啲就精神病有幻覺"},{"pid":"cb5e5e621dd65aa7faa38b11c0570420e9de0a4e","tid":1073954,"uid":97882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:27:04.000Z","msg":"信有鬼都係智力有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a3977545785cf89e213afd765115f8d154eaf6","tid":1073954,"uid":84104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:30:35.000Z","msg":"同同事一齊親眼見過<br />\n所以我信"},{"pid":"d51e564182304e13290b37d0ae61745a3b801d0a","tid":1073954,"uid":166622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"窮人唔怕鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}